# CC‑ Invariants – Formal Specification [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)

This document provides the **complete**, machine-friendly definition of the ten CC‑ tags, including their IDs, human descriptions, canonical check function names in Rust, and failure conditions.  The validator implementation in `core/engine/src/validator.rs` is expected to conform to this specification even though the checks themselves are hard-coded. [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)

***

## Tag: CC-VOL (Volume Lock) [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)

**ID:** `CC-VOL`  
**Check Function:** `check_cc_vol(code: &str, n_min: usize) -> bool`  
**Intent:** Ensure each artifact contains enough concrete code units to be useful in a single iteration. [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)

**Behavior:**  
- Count the number of lines that look like function or structural declarations (`fn`, `pub fn`, `struct`, `impl`, `class`). [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)
- If the count is less than `n_min` (a project-configurable threshold), the check fails. [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)

**Failure Conditions:**  
- `count < n_min` ⇒ `"CC-VOL: Insufficient number of concrete function-like declarations."` [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)

***

## Tag: CC-LANG (Sovereign Stack) [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)

**ID:** `CC-LANG`  
**Check Function:** `check_cc_lang(path: &str) -> bool`  
**Intent:** Restrict artifacts to the sovereign language stack. [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)

**Behavior:**  
- Determine the file extension from the destination path (from `CC-FILE`). [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)
- Accept only: `.rs`, `.js`, `.cpp`, `.h`, `.aln`, `.md`. [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)
- Reject any other extension. [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)

**Failure Conditions:**  
- Extension not in allowed set ⇒ `"CC-LANG: File extension is not part of the sovereign stack."` [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)

***

## Tag: CC-CRATE (Fresh Logic) [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)

**ID:** `CC-CRATE`  
**Check Function:** `check_cc_crate(previous: &HashSet<String>, current: &HashSet<String>) -> bool`  
**Intent:** Guarantee that each iteration introduces at least one new code construct. [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)

**Behavior:**  
- Build a symbol set from the current code using `collect_symbols`, scanning for names after `fn`, `struct`, `impl`, `mod`, and `class`. [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)
- Compare the current symbol set against a previous snapshot (supplied via `ValidationRequest.previous_symbols`). [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)
- Pass if there exists at least one symbol present in `current` but not in `previous`. [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)

**Failure Conditions:**  
- No new symbols found ⇒ `"CC-CRATE: No new symbols introduced compared to previous snapshot."` [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)

***

## Tag: CC-FILE (Destination Strict) [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)

**ID:** `CC-FILE`  
**Check Function:** `extract_file_header_path(code: &str) -> Option<String>`  
**Intent:** Require every file to declare its destination path explicitly. [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)

**Behavior:**  
- Inspect the first 10 lines of the file for a header containing `FILE:`. [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)
- Supported forms include: `// FILE: ./path`, `/* FILE: ./path */`, `<!-- FILE: ./path -->`. [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)
- Extract the substring after `FILE:` as the path, trimming whitespace and optional `=`. [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)
- Pass if a non-empty path is found. [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)

**Failure Conditions:**  
- No valid `FILE:` header in first 10 lines ⇒ `"CC-FILE: Missing FILE header in first lines of file."` [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)

***

## Tag: CC-FULL (No Excerpts) [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)

**ID:** `CC-FULL`  
**Check Function:** `check_cc_full(code: &str) -> bool`  
**Intent:** Forbid truncated or placeholder code. [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)

**Behavior:**  
- Scan the entire file for banned substrings: `"..."`, `"rest of code"`, `"omitted"`. [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)
- Pass only if none of these patterns are present. [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)

**Failure Conditions:**  
- Any banned substring detected ⇒ `"CC-FULL: Found excerpt or placeholder markers in code."` [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)

***

## Tag: CC-DEEP (Depth‑3 Struct) [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)

**ID:** `CC-DEEP`  
**Check Function:** `check_cc_deep(path: &str) -> bool`  
**Intent:** Enforce that core modules reside under at least three path components. [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)

**Behavior:**  
- Normalize the path (collapsing `//`, removing leading `./`). [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)
- Split on `/` and count non-empty segments. [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)
- Pass only if `segments.len() >= 3`. [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)

**Failure Conditions:**  
- `segments.len() < 3` ⇒ `"CC-DEEP: Path does not satisfy depth >= 3 after normalization."` [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)

***

## Tag: CC-ZERO (Zero‑Setup Boot) [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)

**ID:** `CC-ZERO`  
**Check Function:** `check_cc_zero(code: &str) -> bool`  
**Intent:** Prevent any setup/install logic in entrypoints. [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)

**Behavior:**  
- Scan code for banned tokens related to setup or environment: `"install"`, `"setup"`, `"std::env::temp_dir"`, `"std::env::var"`, `"pip "`, `"npm "`, `"yarn "`, `"cargo install"`. [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)
- Pass only if none of these tokens are present. [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)

**Failure Conditions:**  
- Any banned token detected ⇒ `"CC-ZERO: Entry file contains setup/install/environment references."` [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)

***

## Tag: CC-PATH (Path Integrity) [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)

**ID:** `CC-PATH`  
**Check Function:** `check_cc_path(path: &str) -> bool`  
**Intent:** Ensure all paths are portable and well-formed. [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)

**Behavior:**  
- Reject empty paths. [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)
- Reject any path containing `\` (backslash). [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)
- Reject any path containing `"//"` (double slash) after normalization. [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)

**Failure Conditions:**  
- Empty path or contains backslash or double slash ⇒ `"CC-PATH: Path contains backslashes, double slashes, or is empty."` [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)

***

## Tag: CC-SOV (Sovereign Only – No Externals) [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)

**ID:** `CC-SOV`  
**Check Function:** `check_cc_sov(code: &str) -> bool`  
**Intent:** Forbid external crates, tools, or services in core logic. [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)

**Behavior:**  
- For lines that look like imports (`use`, `extern crate`, `#include`, `import`, `require(`), search for banned identifiers: `"reqwest"`, `"serde_json"`, `"openai"`, `"axios"`, `"tree-sitter"`, `"syn"`. [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)
- Pass only if none of these identifiers appear in import-like lines. [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)

**Failure Conditions:**  
- Banned identifier found in an import or include ⇒ `"CC-SOV: Detected external crates, tools, or services in imports."` [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)

***

## Tag: CC-NAV (Custom Navigation Mount Logic) [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)

**ID:** `CC-NAV`  
**Check Function:** `check_cc_nav(code: &str) -> bool`  
**Intent:** Require a custom directory walker instead of external traversal libraries. [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)

**Behavior:**  
- Check for the presence of a function named `walk_dir` (`"fn walk_dir"` or `"pub fn walk_dir"`). [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)
- Additionally require mentions of `"read_dir("` or `"std::fs::read_dir"` to signal actual traversal. [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)
- Reject if lines contain known external walkers like `"walkdir::"` or `"globwalk::"`. [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)
- Pass only if custom `walk_dir` is present, uses `read_dir`, and no external walkers are referenced. [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)

**Failure Conditions:**  
- No `walk_dir` function, no use of `read_dir`, or banned external walkers present ⇒ `"CC-NAV: Custom navigation function not found or external walker detected."` [ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws](https://ppl-ai-file-upload.s3.amazonaws.com/web/direct-files/collection_f23499fa-f1b8-4d9d-a78b-1d96ca262e69/9abc2844-b527-41a6-984d-30e8698958eb/invariants-8Xz_1YHRT1W1xd_tCBpMyA.md)

